sect2.para:
If your image is not made in &susestudio; or &suseonsite;, configure the
image as follows to create an image that can be booted on &kvm; and &xen;,
for example:

listitem.para:
Install the openstack-magnum-k8s-image-x86_64 package. This
package provides a virtual machine image with Kubernetes pre-installed,
openstack-magnum-k8s-image.x86_64.qcow2. &ostack; &o_container;
uses this image when creating clusters with its k8s_opensuse_v1 driver.
